{"tid":944970,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個做過最符合毒撚既野","createTime":"2018-12-17T13:38:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-17T14:28:54.000Z","uid":113705,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b11902d0243960be8a131d1e1909fa3a01ebf82b","tid":944970,"uid":113705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T13:38:41.000Z","msg":"話說考完試上左巴士上層翻屋企, 跟住透過塊玻璃見到有一班唔係好熟既fd上車 (雖然大家都識得,但係裡面有D人讀左幾年都無傾過計)。<br />\n我費事佢地走上上層時比佢地見到，由上層車尾行到去頭嗰排（仲要D人啱啱上車，左穿右插咁行去前排），點知原來佢地企曬喺下層傾計。我原本係提早落車行翻屋企，但係一琳到一落樓梯就見到佢地，一定好尷尬，所以等到巴士去到尾站，等佢地落曬車，先落車，咁樣就唔洗怕比佢地見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係我又要搭翻車翻屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n宜家琳翻都覺得自己毒到出汁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15e48b85c7da5ca06e17d095dc67dc1a2307027f","tid":944970,"uid":153505,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T13:39:58.000Z","msg":"上連燈"},{"pid":"1132b06ae50a421432192568dda8716224a94e35","tid":944970,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T14:28:41.000Z","msg":"做喺女神隔籬唔敢出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d99f1843a5ff8037df7887fd28b1057af49cb6be","tid":944970,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T14:28:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">坐</span>喺女神隔籬唔敢出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"}]}